Package: nirs4alldatasets
Title: Acquire Curated NIRS Reference Datasets (nirs4all-datasets)
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Gregory", "Beurier", email = "beurier@cirad.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R binding over the nirs4all-datasets C ABI (n4ds_*): resolve a dataset id
    from the distributable catalog index into a version-pinned download contract,
    fetch the canonical Parquet (Dataverse / Zenodo / figshare) with SHA-256
    verification into a local cache, and re-verify a cached directory offline. JSON
    crosses the stable C ABI; analysis of the data is left to the host.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: Cargo (the Rust toolchain) to build the bundled core; see cran-comments.md.
